description:
State of the process. Valid values: `draft`, `publishing`, `pending`, `done`, `cancelled`, `finalizing` or `error`.
It can be:
- `draft`: the process is not published, - `publishing`: publication started and is ongoing, - `pending`: tasks need to be completed, - `done`: all tasks have been completed, - `cancelled`: the process has been cancelled, - `finalizing`: post process actions are being executed, - `error`: errors have occurred during finalization.
